      <div class="txt">A genuine, well-positioned defence-electronics growth story with a 2.5&times;-revenue order book and large operating-leverage runway &mdash; but priced for perfection at ~57&times; earnings while reported profits are <strong>not</strong> converting to cash. We like the franchise, not the entry price.</div>
